    "In contrast, 19 studies used a CNN model to improve the detection accuracy of malicious clients.",
    "These studies (Liu et al. 2023b; Bin et al. 2023; Jia et al. 2024; Andreina et al. 2021; Man et al. 2021) excel in feature extraction and have demonstrated significant improvements, as shown in Table 6.",
